snippet.title: Riders of Rohan gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Riders of Rohan (aka j.r.r. tolkien's riders of rohan), Dos PC game produced by Konami in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/riders-of-rohan/1636/
Exploring and engaging in combat in this fantasy adventure based on the classic stories.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Rorke's Drift - https://youtu.be/2K6fg9qA5QE
Morkin 2 - https://youtu.be/GEd2LZhWpBQ
Charge of The Light Brigade - https://youtu.be/N6mvhnyKKKk
